            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Though called \u201cthe spawn of the Eshtayiv,\u201d pyricharbingers are the constituents of this entity rather thanits offspring. These rare creatures travel through space tofind dark places to illuminate and beings to slay, creatingterror and pyric undead.<br/><br/>A pyric harbinger looks like an orb of fire, but within thatflame is a gelatinous sphere that is 5 feet in diameter andmostly maw. Those who\u2019ve studied a harbinger\u2019s ashy remainsestimate they weigh only 100 pounds."
        }
